Since you seem to have not read the rest of the thread, I'll break it down for you.
<br />

<br />
During Kunark, pets took ripostes.  On a riposte, it is possible for the mob to use its innate proc.  Venril Sathir (innately) procs a 1500 point lifetap.  Therefore, if the pet was riposted, it is possible that Venril Sathir could be healed for 1500 damage.<br />_________________<br />Altanis Blazewielder
