VS wont get taps off on runed players, keep rune on pet the whole time and he wont do dmg, his tap is an innate proc not weapon proc so it depends on if he hits, and he has a high chance of lifetapping when he hits. i dont know if he is stunnable, i dont think he was, if he is then WoX would defnitely be good there. also i agree that MR is useless, our tank had 400 MR and said that it hit full on him each time. good luck to anyone who takes him, and grats if someone takes him down.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
You will not be landing any Magic spells on VS (stuns) so forget Air pet stun or Earth Pet root.  Or Enchanter nukes or Cleric nukes.  Or Black Steel.  You can land Mala on him, but you still will never land any magic spells on him.  I don't know if he's slowable, but we never tried becuase he's a Manaetic Behemoth type fight (dead in 1.5-2 min, if even that).  I will say no Enchanter or bard will be slowing him if he is.  Oh no BL either.  Had a necro say in channel he slowed VS /laugh
<br />

<br />
There was much more to VS than just putting everyone in back of him.  VS agro is proximity agro (he is Undead).  If a rogue got closer to him than the main tank, gratz rogue on healing VS (since the main strat back then was chain rune since Enchanters are essentially useless other than rune on VS).  With VS regen coupled with Deadly lifetap, it was essential for all other melee to stay at max melee range, or it could be a quick wipe.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Aweee, did Mister Meanie Inkie come gank you and take your spawn? Would you like a tissue? Oh you think that if you spam him for the next hour calling him every hostile word in your petty little head that you are going to upset him? Bluebie Please.</span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
